---
const {
	title = "价值试算工具",
	description = "把文章中的 DCF 变体公式拆成可调参数，直接观察 NOI、估值区间和挂牌价偏离程度。",
} = Astro.props;
---

<section class="valuation-lab" aria-labelledby="valuation-lab-title">
	<div class="valuation-lab__header">
		<div>
			<p class="valuation-lab__eyebrow">Interactive Lab</p>
			<h4 id="valuation-lab-title">{title}</h4>
			<p class="valuation-lab__description">{description}</p>
		</div>
		<div class="valuation-lab__formula">
			<div class="valuation-formula" aria-label="V equals NOI over r_f plus r_p minus g, plus U">
				<span class="valuation-formula__symbol">V</span>
				<span class="valuation-formula__symbol">=</span>
				<span class="valuation-formula__fraction">
					<span class="valuation-formula__numerator">NOI</span>
					<span class="valuation-formula__denominator">r_f + r_p - g</span>
				</span>
				<span class="valuation-formula__symbol">+</span>
				<span class="valuation-formula__symbol">U</span>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="valuation-lab__layout">
		<div class="valuation-lab__panel">
			<h5>现金流假设</h5>
			<div class="valuation-lab__grid">
				<label class="valuation-field">
					<span>月租金</span>
					<div class="valuation-field__control">
						<input id="pc-rent" type="number" min="0" step="100" value="4500" />
						<em>元 / 月</em>
					</div>
				</label>

				<label class="valuation-field valuation-field--wide">
					<span>年度运营成本</span>
					<div class="valuation-field__control">
						<input id="pc-cost" type="number" min="0" step="1000" value="4000" />
						<em>元 / 年</em>
					</div>
					<small>可理解为维修、税费、中介、家具折旧等长期平均成本。</small>
				</label>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="valuation-lab__panel">
			<h5>估值参数</h5>
			<div class="valuation-lab__grid">
				<label class="valuation-field">
					<span>无风险利率 r_f</span>
					<div class="valuation-field__control">
						<input id="pc-rf" type="number" min="0" max="20" step="0.1" value="1.8" />
						<em>%</em>
					</div>
				</label>

				<label class="valuation-field">
					<span>风险溢价 r_p</span>
					<div class="valuation-field__control">
						<input id="pc-rp" type="number" min="0" max="20" step="0.1" value="1.0" />
						<em>%</em>
					</div>
				</label>

				<label class="valuation-field">
					<span>长期增长 g</span>
					<div class="valuation-field__control">
						<input id="pc-g" type="number" min="-5" max="10" step="0.1" value="0" />
						<em>%</em>
					</div>
				</label>

				<label class="valuation-field">
					<span>附加价值 U</span>
					<div class="valuation-field__control">
						<input id="pc-u" type="number" min="0" step="1" value="50" />
						<em>万元</em>
					</div>
				</label>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="valuation-lab__compare">
		<label class="valuation-field valuation-field--wide">
			<span>市场对照价格</span>
			<div class="valuation-field__control">
				<input id="pc-price" type="number" min="0" step="1" value="300" />
				<em>万元</em>
			</div>
			<small>输入你正在看的成交价或挂牌价，直接比较当前定价是折价还是溢价。</small>
		</label>
	</div>

	<div class="valuation-lab__metrics">
		<article class="metric-card metric-card--primary">
			<span class="metric-card__label">估算真实价值</span>
			<strong class="metric-card__value"><span id="pc-value">228.57</span> 万元</strong>
			<p class="metric-card__hint">基于当前 NOI、折现率与附加价值综合估算。</p>
		</article>

		<article class="metric-card">
			<span class="metric-card__label">NOI</span>
			<strong class="metric-card__value"><span id="pc-noi">5.13</span> 万元</strong>
			<p class="metric-card__hint">年租金扣除运营成本后的净经营收入。</p>
		</article>

		<article class="metric-card">
			<span class="metric-card__label">挂牌价偏离</span>
			<strong class="metric-card__value"><span id="pc-gap">71.43</span> 万元</strong>
			<p class="metric-card__hint"><span id="pc-gap-rate">31.25%</span> 的溢价/折价幅度。</p>
		</article>
	</div>

	<div class="valuation-lab__summary">
		<div>
			<span class="valuation-badge" id="pc-badge">当前偏贵</span>
			<p id="pc-summary">
				以当前假设看，挂牌价高于模型估值，意味着买方在为未来增长预期或更高的无形价值支付额外溢价。
			</p>
		</div>
		<ul class="valuation-lab__bullets">
			<li><span>资本化折现率</span><strong id="pc-discount">2.80%</strong></li>
			<li><span>租售比倒数</span><strong id="pc-payback">58.5 年</strong></li>
			<li><span>安全边际价格</span><strong id="pc-margin">205.71 万元</strong></li>
		</ul>
	</div>

	<p class="valuation-lab__warning" id="pc-warning" hidden>
		当 g 接近或高于 r_f + r_p 时，模型会失真。此时应下调增长率，或提高风险溢价后再看结果。
	</p>
</section>

<script>
	if (typeof window !== "undefined") {
		const initPropertyCalculator = () => {
			const ids = [
				"pc-rent",
				"pc-cost",
				"pc-rf",
				"pc-rp",
				"pc-g",
				"pc-u",
				"pc-price",
			];

			const inputs = ids
				.map((id) => document.getElementById(id))
				.filter((element): element is HTMLInputElement => element instanceof HTMLInputElement);
			if (inputs.length !== ids.length) return;

			const valueNode = document.getElementById("pc-value");
			const noiNode = document.getElementById("pc-noi");
			const gapNode = document.getElementById("pc-gap");
			const gapRateNode = document.getElementById("pc-gap-rate");
			const badgeNode = document.getElementById("pc-badge");
			const summaryNode = document.getElementById("pc-summary");
			const discountNode = document.getElementById("pc-discount");
			const paybackNode = document.getElementById("pc-payback");
			const marginNode = document.getElementById("pc-margin");
			const warningNode = document.getElementById("pc-warning");

			if (
				!valueNode ||
				!noiNode ||
				!gapNode ||
				!gapRateNode ||
				!badgeNode ||
				!summaryNode ||
				!discountNode ||
				!paybackNode ||
				!marginNode ||
				!warningNode
			) {
				return;
			}

			const read = (id: string) => {
				const element = document.getElementById(id);
				if (!(element instanceof HTMLInputElement)) return 0;
				return Number.parseFloat(element.value) || 0;
			};

			const formatWan = (value: number) => value.toFixed(2);
			const formatPercent = (value: number) => `${value.toFixed(2)}%`;

			const update = () => {
				const monthlyRent = read("pc-rent");
				const annualCost = read("pc-cost");
				const rf = read("pc-rf") / 100;
				const rp = read("pc-rp") / 100;
				const g = read("pc-g") / 100;
				const utilityValue = read("pc-u") * 10000;
				const askingPriceWan = read("pc-price");
				const askingPrice = askingPriceWan * 10000;

				const annualRent = monthlyRent * 12;
				const noi = Math.max(annualRent - annualCost, 0);
				const discountRate = rf + rp - g;

				const invalidModel = discountRate <= 0;
				const fairValue = invalidModel ? 0 : noi / discountRate + utilityValue;
				const gap = askingPrice - fairValue;
				const gapRate = fairValue > 0 ? (gap / fairValue) * 100 : 0;
				const paybackYears = noi > 0 ? askingPrice / noi : 0;
				const safetyMargin = fairValue * 0.9;

				valueNode.textContent = formatWan(fairValue / 10000);
				noiNode.textContent = formatWan(noi / 10000);
				gapNode.textContent = formatWan(Math.abs(gap) / 10000);
				gapRateNode.textContent = formatPercent(Math.abs(gapRate));
				discountNode.textContent = formatPercent(discountRate * 100);
				paybackNode.textContent = paybackYears > 0 ? `${paybackYears.toFixed(1)} 年` : "不可用";
				marginNode.textContent = `${formatWan(safetyMargin / 10000)} 万元`;
				warningNode.hidden = !invalidModel;

				if (invalidModel) {
					badgeNode.textContent = "参数失真";
					badgeNode.dataset.state = "warn";
					summaryNode.textContent =
						"增长率已经接近或高于折现率，模型分母失真，当前结果不具参考性。建议提高风险溢价或下调增长假设。";
					return;
				}

				if (gapRate >= 0.15) {
					badgeNode.textContent = "当前偏贵";
					badgeNode.dataset.state = "hot";
					summaryNode.textContent =
						"挂牌价明显高于模型估值，除非你对未来租金增长、地段溢价或学区价值有更强判断，否则安全边际偏薄。";
				} else if (gapRate <= -0.1) {
					badgeNode.textContent = "存在折价";
					badgeNode.dataset.state = "cool";
					summaryNode.textContent =
						"挂牌价低于模型估值，说明现金流回报与附加价值对价格形成了支撑，属于值得继续做尽调的区间。";
				} else {
					badgeNode.textContent = "接近合理";
					badgeNode.dataset.state = "neutral";
					summaryNode.textContent =
						"挂牌价与模型估值接近，更多取决于你对未来增长、流动性和城市长期竞争力的判断。";
				}
			};

			inputs.forEach((input) => input.addEventListener("input", update));
			update();
		};

		if (document.readyState === "loading") {
			document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", initPropertyCalculator, { once: true });
		} else {
			initPropertyCalculator();
		}
	}
</script>

<style>
	.valuation-lab {
		margin: 2rem 0;
		padding: 1.5rem;
		border-radius: 1.25rem;
		border: 1px solid color-mix(in oklab, var(--primary) 12%, var(--line-divider));
		background:
			radial-gradient(circle at top right, color-mix(in oklab, var(--primary) 10%, transparent), transparent 30%),
			linear-gradient(180deg, color-mix(in oklab, var(--card-bg) 92%, white 8%), var(--card-bg));
		box-shadow: 0 18px 40px rgb(15 23 42 / 0.08);
	}

	.valuation-lab__header {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: space-between;
		gap: 1rem;
		align-items: flex-start;
		margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
	}

	.valuation-lab__eyebrow {
		margin: 0 0 0.35rem;
		font-size: 0.72rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		letter-spacing: 0.16em;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		color: var(--primary);
	}

	.valuation-lab h4,
	.valuation-lab h5,
	.valuation-lab p {
		margin: 0;
	}

	.valuation-lab h4 {
		font-size: 1.35rem;
	}

	.valuation-lab__description {
		margin-top: 0.45rem;
		color: var(--text-muted);
		line-height: 1.65;
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		max-width: 42rem;
	}

	.valuation-lab__formula {
		padding: 0.75rem 0.9rem;
		border-radius: 0.95rem;
		background: color-mix(in oklab, var(--primary) 8%, transparent);
		color: var(--primary);
		font-weight: 700;
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		white-space: nowrap;
	}

	.valuation-formula {
		display: inline-flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 0.45rem;
	}

	.valuation-formula__symbol {
		font-size: 1.05rem;
	}

	.valuation-formula__fraction {
		display: inline-flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		align-items: center;
		line-height: 1.1;
	}

	.valuation-formula__numerator {
		padding: 0 0.55rem 0.2rem;
		border-bottom: 1.5px solid currentColor;
	}

	.valuation-formula__denominator {
		padding-top: 0.18rem;
		font-size: 0.88rem;
	}

	.valuation-lab__layout {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
		gap: 1rem;
	}

	.valuation-lab__compare {
		margin-top: 1rem;
		padding: 1rem;
		border-radius: 1rem;
		background: color-mix(in oklab, var(--primary) 4%, var(--card-bg));
		border: 1px solid color-mix(in oklab, var(--primary) 8%, var(--line-divider));
	}

	.valuation-lab__panel {
		padding: 1rem;
		border-radius: 1rem;
		background: color-mix(in oklab, var(--card-bg) 88%, white 12%);
		border: 1px solid color-mix(in oklab, var(--primary) 8%, var(--line-divider));
	}

	.valuation-lab__panel h5 {
		font-size: 0.98rem;
		margin-bottom: 0.9rem;
	}

	.valuation-lab__grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
		gap: 0.9rem;
	}

	.valuation-field {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 0.45rem;
	}

	.valuation-field--wide {
		grid-column: 1 / -1;
	}

	.valuation-field span {
		font-size: 0.88rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		color: var(--text-muted);
	}

	.valuation-field small {
		font-size: 0.78rem;
		line-height: 1.5;
		color: var(--text-muted);
	}

	.valuation-field__control {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 0.65rem;
		padding: 0.2rem 0.75rem;
		min-height: 3rem;
		border-radius: 0.9rem;
		border: 1px solid color-mix(in oklab, var(--primary) 10%, var(--line-divider));
		background: color-mix(in oklab, var(--card-bg) 92%, white 8%);
	}

	.valuation-field__control:focus-within {
		border-color: color-mix(in oklab, var(--primary) 30%, var(--line-divider));
		box-shadow: 0 0 0 0.2rem color-mix(in oklab, var(--primary) 12%, transparent);
	}

	.valuation-field input {
		width: 100%;
		min-width: 0;
		border: 0;
		background: transparent;
		font: inherit;
		font-size: 1rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		color: var(--text-normal);
		outline: none;
	}

	.valuation-field__control em {
		font-style: normal;
		font-size: 0.82rem;
		white-space: nowrap;
		color: var(--text-muted);
	}

	.valuation-lab__metrics {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
		gap: 1rem;
		margin-top: 1rem;
	}

	.metric-card {
		padding: 1rem;
		border-radius: 1rem;
		background: color-mix(in oklab, var(--card-bg) 90%, white 10%);
		border: 1px solid color-mix(in oklab, var(--primary) 8%, var(--line-divider));
	}

	.metric-card--primary {
		background:
			linear-gradient(135deg, color-mix(in oklab, var(--primary) 12%, var(--card-bg)), color-mix(in oklab, var(--primary) 4%, var(--card-bg)));
		border-color: color-mix(in oklab, var(--primary) 22%, var(--line-divider));
	}

	.metric-card__label {
		display: block;
		font-size: 0.82rem;
		color: var(--text-muted);
		margin-bottom: 0.55rem;
	}

	.metric-card__value {
		display: block;
		font-size: 1.55rem;
		line-height: 1.15;
	}

	.metric-card__hint {
		margin-top: 0.55rem;
		font-size: 0.82rem;
		line-height: 1.55;
		color: var(--text-muted);
	}

	.valuation-lab__summary {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.4fr) minmax(18rem, 1fr);
		gap: 1rem;
		align-items: start;
		margin-top: 1rem;
		padding: 1rem;
		border-radius: 1rem;
		background: color-mix(in oklab, var(--primary) 4%, var(--card-bg));
		border: 1px solid color-mix(in oklab, var(--primary) 8%, var(--line-divider));
	}

	.valuation-badge {
		display: inline-flex;
		align-items: center;
		padding: 0.35rem 0.7rem;
		border-radius: 999px;
		font-size: 0.78rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
		background: color-mix(in oklab, var(--primary) 12%, transparent);
		color: var(--primary);
	}

	.valuation-badge[data-state="hot"] {
		background: rgb(239 68 68 / 0.12);
		color: rgb(220 38 38);
	}

	.valuation-badge[data-state="cool"] {
		background: rgb(14 165 233 / 0.12);
		color: rgb(3 105 161);
	}

	.valuation-badge[data-state="warn"] {
		background: rgb(245 158 11 / 0.12);
		color: rgb(180 83 9);
	}

	.valuation-lab__summary p {
		line-height: 1.7;
		color: var(--text-normal);
	}

	.valuation-lab__bullets {
		list-style: none;
		margin: 0;
		padding: 0;
		display: grid;
		gap: 0.75rem;
	}

	.valuation-lab__bullets li {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: space-between;
		gap: 1rem;
		padding: 0.85rem 0.9rem;
		border-radius: 0.9rem;
		background: color-mix(in oklab, var(--card-bg) 92%, white 8%);
		border: 1px solid color-mix(in oklab, var(--primary) 8%, var(--line-divider));
	}

	.valuation-lab__bullets span {
		font-size: 0.88rem;
		color: var(--text-muted);
	}

	.valuation-lab__bullets strong {
		font-size: 0.98rem;
	}

	.valuation-lab__warning {
		margin-top: 0.9rem;
		padding: 0.85rem 1rem;
		border-radius: 0.9rem;
		border: 1px solid rgb(245 158 11 / 0.2);
		background: rgb(245 158 11 / 0.08);
		color: rgb(180 83 9);
		font-size: 0.88rem;
		line-height: 1.6;
	}

	:root.dark .valuation-lab {
		box-shadow: 0 18px 40px rgb(2 6 23 / 0.28);
	}

	:root.dark .valuation-badge[data-state="hot"] {
		color: rgb(252 165 165);
	}

	:root.dark .valuation-badge[data-state="cool"] {
		color: rgb(125 211 252);
	}

	:root.dark .valuation-badge[data-state="warn"] {
		color: rgb(253 186 116);
	}

	@media (max-width: 960px) {
		.valuation-lab__layout,
		.valuation-lab__metrics,
		.valuation-lab__summary {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}
	}

	@media (max-width: 640px) {
		.valuation-lab {
			padding: 1rem;
		}

		.valuation-lab__header,
		.valuation-lab__grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}

		.valuation-lab__header {
			display: grid;
		}

		.valuation-lab__formula {
			white-space: normal;
		}
	}
</style>
